				<title>SCP-5057 Additional Documentation</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/the-good-ending</link>
				<description>


&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Addendum 5057.3&lt;/strong&gt; SCP-5057 was successfully transferred to the recently formed Professor Funtastic Researcher Team lead by Dr. Cole. The following interviews/interactions were recorded by Dr. Cole and the GoI-563&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-795406-1&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; research team.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;align:left; margin-top: 10px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;hcole@scp.int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;jeverwood@scp.int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subject:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;SCP-5057&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sorry to bother you; I know you are very busy but I had an inquiry about SCP-5057 and its time spent under your care. In your assistant&#039;s notes it says it is very chatty and childlike, but when we spoke it gave one-word answers and shooed me out of its containment chamber.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did something happen to it that wasn&#039;t documented while it was under your care?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks in advance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr. H. Cole&lt;br /&gt;
GoI-563 Research Lead&lt;br /&gt;
Secure, Contain, Protect&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;align:left; margin-top: 10px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;jeverwood@scp.int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;hcole@scp.int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subject:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;RE:SCP-5057&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Harry,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I did not personally interact with SCP-5057 while it was assigned to my department. My assistant Rex Alces was in charge of it. I will ask him shortly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr. J. Everwood&lt;br /&gt;
GoI-466 Research Lead&lt;br /&gt;
Secure, Contain, Protect&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;lt;BEGIN LOG&amp;gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Hello, fifty-fifty-seven. I see you are painting again.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Art is purpose. Takes mind off toxicity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Well, I&#039;m glad you&#039;ve got something to help improve your mental state. And speaking of your mental state, that&#039;s why I&#039;m here. I wanted to check in on you and see how you were doing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;[SCP-5057 stops painting and turns to face Dr. Cole.]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; I is feeling toxic. I cannot be eaten by the good little boys and girls because I am toxic. So I make art. But art is not enough. So I make more art.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Yeah, I can see you&#039;ve been busy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Yeah. Does you needing anything else? Should not be speaking to me because I am toxic to eat and be talking to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; What do you mean you&#039;re toxic to be spoken to?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; I is make friend but friend become mean and no longer friend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; I&#039;m not sure I fully understand what you mean.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Is because I am stupid little plastic failure of child product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; What? Where did you get that from?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;[There is a five second silence. SCP-5057 turns around and continues painting on its canvas.]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; What did you mean by that?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Please do not be of talking to me. I am toxic to eat and be talking to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;[Dr. Cole approaches SCP-5057 and inspects the canvas it is working on.]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Hmm. Okay. I think I get it now. I&#039;ll be back later, fifty-fifty-seven.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Okay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;align:left; margin-top: 10px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;jeverwood@scp.int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
