&lt;p&gt;Harry,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My assistant said he is familiar with the portrait but reports no unusual events surrounding it. However, he seemed rather uncomfortable about the situation and appeared apprehensive to answer. Therefore I will be personally combing through the logs of all recorded interactions between SCP-5057 and my assistant. I will report any findings to you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;/p&gt;
