&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;lt;BEGIN LOG&amp;gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Hello, fifty-fifty-seven.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Hello! I am of feeling very very good.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; That&#039;s great! What turned your mood around?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; I spend time wondering &#039;what if I is make people toxic?&#039; But you are say I am not toxic, only to eat. I am perfectly fine you say! So I spend time wondering &#039;what if what Doctor Cole are say is right?&#039; And then I feel good. I have not feel good since Rex was friend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Heh. I&#039;m glad you&#039;re feeling better then. By the way, I think you&#039;ll be receiving something from your old &#039;friend&#039; Rex.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Why is?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Just call it a hunch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Okay, I is calling it hunch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; So do you want to show me what you painted today?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Yes! Behold!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;[SCP-5054 steps towards a canvas towards the back of its containment chamber and returns with with it, handing it to Dr. Cole.]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Very nice. Are you done with it?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Yes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Perfect. Why don&#039;t I hang it up for you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Yes!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;[Dr. Cole proceeds to place the canvas on the wall, hung by a present nail.]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; There we go. So, now that we&#039;ve got that out of the way, why don&#039;t we talk a little about Professor Funtastic?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Okay, but I ask one thing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; What is it?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Can you be of calling me &#039;Taste&#039;?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cole:&lt;/strong&gt; Anything you want, Taste.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCP-5057:&lt;/strong&gt; Okay. I be telling you everything I know now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;lt;END LOG&amp;gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; SCP-5057 was questioned for 2 hours following this interaction but was unable to provide any information on Professor Funtastic. Further research is currently pending.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
