&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: green&quot;&gt;Purposeful emotional manipulation of a sentient SCP object violates Ethics Committee Decree #1221-A. Further infractions will be met with termination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: blue&quot;&gt;This level of unprofessional behavior is unacceptable. I expected better from someone I trust enough to be my second in command. I expect you to apologize to SCP-5057 as well.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
