					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: right;"></div> <p><strong>Addendum 5057.3</strong> SCP-5057 was successfully transferred to the recently formed Professor Funtastic Researcher Team lead by Dr. Cole. The following interviews/interactions were recorded by Dr. Cole and the GoI-563<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-195806-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> research team.<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);"> <table style="align:left; margin-top: 10px;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>From:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">hcole@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>To:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">jeverwood@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>Subject:</strong></th> <td>SCP-5057</td> </tr> </table> <hr /> <p>Hello,</p> <p>Sorry to bother you; I know you are very busy but I had an inquiry about SCP-5057 and its time spent under your care. In your assistant's notes it says it is very chatty and childlike, but when we spoke it gave one-word answers and shooed me out of its containment chamber.</p> <p>Did something happen to it that wasn't documented while it was under your care?</p> <p>Thanks in advance.</p> <hr /> <p>Dr. H. Cole<br /> GoI-563 Research Lead<br /> Secure, Contain, Protect</p> </div> <div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);"> <table style="align:left; margin-top: 10px;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>From:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">jeverwood@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>To:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">hcole@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>Subject:</strong></th> <td>RE:SCP-5057</td> </tr> </table> <hr /> <p>Harry,</p> <p>I did not personally interact with SCP-5057 while it was assigned to my department. My assistant Rex Alces was in charge of it. I will ask him shortly.</p> <p>Regards,</p> <hr /> <p>Dr. J. Everwood<br /> GoI-466 Research Lead<br /> Secure, Contain, Protect</p> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>&lt;BEGIN LOG&gt;</strong></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Hello, fifty-fifty-seven. I see you are painting again.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Art is purpose. Takes mind off toxicity.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Well, I'm glad you've got something to help improve your mental state. And speaking of your mental state, that's why I'm here. I wanted to check in on you and see how you were doing.</p> <p><em>[SCP-5057 stops painting and turns to face Dr. Cole.]</em></p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I is feeling toxic. I cannot be eaten by the good little boys and girls because I am toxic. So I make art. But art is not enough. So I make more art.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Yeah, I can see you've been busy.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Yeah. Does you needing anything else? Should not be speaking to me because I am toxic to eat and be talking to.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> What do you mean you're toxic to be spoken to?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I is make friend but friend become mean and no longer friend.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> I'm not sure I fully understand what you mean.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Is because I am stupid little plastic failure of child product.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> What? Where did you get that from?</p> <p><em>[There is a five second silence. SCP-5057 turns around and continues painting on its canvas.]</em></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> What did you mean by that?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Please do not be of talking to me. I am toxic to eat and be talking to.</p> <p><em>[Dr. Cole approaches SCP-5057 and inspects the canvas it is working on.]</em></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Hmm. Okay. I think I get it now. I'll be back later, fifty-fifty-seven.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay.</p> </blockquote> <div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);"> <table style="align:left; margin-top: 10px;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>From:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">jeverwood@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>To:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">hcole@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>Subject:</strong></th> <td>RE:SCP-5057</td> </tr> </table> <hr /> <p>Harry,</p> <p>I checked with my assistant and he says nothing out of the norm occurred to SCP-5057 during its time here. Sorry we could not be of further assistance to your research.</p> <p>Regards,</p> <hr /> <p>Dr. J. Everwood<br /> GoI-466 Research Lead<br /> Secure, Contain, Protect</p> </div> <div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);"> <table style="align:left; margin-top: 10px;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>From:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">hcole@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>To:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">jeverwood@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>Subject:</strong></th> <td>SCP-5057</td> </tr> </table> <hr /> <p>Hello,</p> <p>I believe you should question your assistant again regarding the attached document.</p> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-good-ending/smudge.jpg" alt="smudge.jpg" class="image" /> <p>Thanks in advance.</p> <hr /> <p>Dr. H. Cole<br /> GoI-563 Research Lead<br /> Secure, Contain, Protect</p> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>&lt;BEGIN LOG&gt;</strong></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Hi, fifty-fifty-seven. How are you feeling?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> The same.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> I'm sorry you're not feeling well, but I'd like to talk to you about what happened.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Researcher Rex, how did he treat you?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Rex was friend. Yeah. Good friend.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Then why did you do that to the portrait of you two?</p> <p><em>[Dr. Cole points to the portrait of Researcher Rex and SCP-5057.]</em></p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I am not wanting to talk about it.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Was he cruel to you?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> What is cruel?</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Hmm. Being cruel is like being really mean and unfriendly to someone.</p> <p><em>[There is a ten-second silence.]</em></p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Yes. He was of being cruel.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> What did he do?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> He made me feel toxic.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> I see. For what it's worth, I don't think you're toxic to talk to, fify-fifty-seven.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Really?</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Yeah. You seem like an alright person who was mistreated and lead to believe something that isn't true.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> But I am still toxic.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> You may be toxic to eat, but you are not a toxic person. If anything, I believe Researcher Rex is the real toxic person here.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I am&#8230; not toxic?</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> No. You're you. And that's perfectly fine. You know, a real friend wouldn't make you feel toxic. A real friend cares about what you have to say and actually listens to you.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I am me&#8230; I am not knowing of what to say.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> You don't need to say anything. Why don't you go ahead and paint something new? I have to get in contact with someone about something.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay!</p> <p><strong>&lt;END LOG&gt;</strong></p> </blockquote> <div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/SCP_icon%281%29.png) top right no-repeat; float: center; border: solid 3px #444444; width: 85%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);"> <table style="align:left; margin-top: 10px;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>From:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">jeverwood@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>To:</strong></th> <td><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">hcole@scp.int</span></span></td> </tr> <tr> <th style="text-align:right"><strong>Subject:</strong></th> <td>RE:SCP-5057</td> </tr> </table> <hr /> <p>Harry,</p> <p>My assistant said he is familiar with the portrait but reports no unusual events surrounding it. However, he seemed rather uncomfortable about the situation and appeared apprehensive to answer. Therefore I will be personally combing through the logs of all recorded interactions between SCP-5057 and my assistant. I will report any findings to you.</p> <p>Regards,</p> <hr /> <p>Dr. J. Everwood<br /> GoI-466 Research Lead<br /> Secure, Contain, Protect</p> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>&lt;BEGIN LOG&gt;</strong></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Hello, fifty-fifty-seven.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Hello! I am of feeling very very good.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> That's great! What turned your mood around?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> I spend time wondering 'what if I is make people toxic?' But you are say I am not toxic, only to eat. I am perfectly fine you say! So I spend time wondering 'what if what Doctor Cole are say is right?' And then I feel good. I have not feel good since Rex was friend.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Heh. I'm glad you're feeling better then. By the way, I think you'll be receiving something from your old 'friend' Rex.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Why is?</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Just call it a hunch.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay, I is calling it hunch.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> So do you want to show me what you painted today?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Yes! Behold!</p> <p><em>[SCP-5054 steps towards a canvas towards the back of its containment chamber and returns with with it, handing it to Dr. Cole.]</em></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Very nice. Are you done with it?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Yes.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Perfect. Why don't I hang it up for you?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Yes!</p> <p><em>[Dr. Cole proceeds to place the canvas on the wall, hung by a present nail.]</em></p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> There we go. So, now that we've got that out of the way, why don't we talk a little about Professor Funtastic?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay, but I ask one thing.</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> What is it?</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Can you be of calling me 'Taste'?</p> <p><strong>Cole:</strong> Anything you want, Taste.</p> <p><strong>SCP-5057:</strong> Okay. I be telling you everything I know now.</p> <p><strong>&lt;END LOG&gt;</strong></p> <p><em><strong>Note:</strong> SCP-5057 was questioned for 2 hours following this interaction but was unable to provide any information on Professor Funtastic. Further research is currently pending.</em></p> </blockquote> <div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-good-ending/perfectlyfine.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="perfectlyfine.jpg" class="image" /> <div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;"> <p>Portrait produced by SCP-5057.</p> </div> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <blockquote> <h4><span>NOTICE OF DISCIPLINARY WARNING</span></h4> <p>This notice indicates that I, <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: red">REX ALCES</span></em></span>, have been informed by <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: green">THE ETHICS COMMITTEE</span></em></span> of recent rule-breaking behavior. I, <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: red">REX ALCES</span></em></span>, agree to not repeat this behavior under threat of further disciplinary action.</p> <p>ETHICS COMMITTEE LIAISON SIGNATURE:</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: green">K. INADA</span></em></span></p> <p>SUPERVISOR SIGNATURE:</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: blue">J. EVERWOOD</span></em></span></p> <p>PENALTY:</p> <p>Docking of monthly pay (TBD).</p> <p>NOTES:<br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: green">Purposeful emotional manipulation of a sentient SCP object violates Ethics Committee Decree #1221-A. Further infractions will be met with termination.</span></em></span></p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="color: blue">This level of unprofessional behavior is unacceptable. I expected better from someone I trust enough to be my second in command. I expect you to apologize to SCP-5057 as well.</span></em></span></p> </blockquote> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div class="page"> <p><span style="font-size:125%;">Dear SCP-5057,<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> I am sorry. I shouldn't have treated you the way I did. That wasn't very friend-like of me and I sincerely hope you're being treated better wherever you are now.<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> - Rex.</span></p> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <div class="page"> <p><em><span style="font-family: 'Reenie Beanie'; font-size: 50px;">is ok</span></em><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <em><span style="font-family: 'Reenie Beanie'; font-size: 50px;">- Señor Taste</span></em></p> </div> </div> <div class="licensebox"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">‡&nbsp;Licensing&nbsp;/&nbsp;Citation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">‡&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;Licensing&nbsp;/&nbsp;Citation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Cite this page as:</p> <p>For more information, see <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/licensing-guide">Licensing Guide</a>.<br /> <strong>Licensing Disclosures</strong></p> <div class="content-separator" style="display: none:"></div> <blockquote> <p><strong>Filename:</strong> smudge.jpg<br /> <strong>Name:</strong> smudge<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2551139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226467" alt="pastarasta1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2551139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" >pastarasta1</a></span><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY SA 3.0<br /> <strong>Source Link:</strong> N/A</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><strong>Filename:</strong> perfectlyfine.jpg<br /> <strong>Name:</strong> perfectlyfine<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2551139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226467" alt="pastarasta1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2551139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" >pastarasta1</a></span><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY SA 3.0<br /> <strong>Source Link:</strong> N/A</p> </blockquote> <div class="content-separator" style="display: none:"></div> <div class="content-separator" style="display: none:"></div> <p>For more information about on-wiki content, visit the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/licensing-master-list">Licensing Master List</a>.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226467" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-195806-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. Professor Funtastic.</div> </div> 
