&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Footnotes&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-653274-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;. SCP-5965&#039;s original corpse has remained present within its coffin since burial.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-653274-2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;2&lt;/a&gt;. Between 5 and 6 years of age.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-653274-3&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;3&lt;/a&gt;. All sessions were covertly recorded. Transcripts available on request.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
