ic in search of similar messages and scan them for potential cognitohazards.</p> <p><strong>Description:</strong> SCP-5922 is a cognitohazardous message capable of inducing heart failure in a subject that perceives it. SCP-5922 was discovered after an event that occurred on 2020/09/22 and caused the deaths of eleven individuals between the ages of 18 and 26 in a period of 7 minutes. All subjects were found to have been communicating in an online chat room at the time of death.</p> <p>On 2020/09/25, containment teams located Alexandre Castro, a non-anomalous civilian involved in the incident. Mr. Castro was found in a state of considerable psychological distress, and has since been amnesticized and provided with grief counseling.</p> <hr /> <p><strong>Addendum 5922.01:</strong> Chat Log Transcript</p> <div class="discord"> <div class="messages-panel"> <div class="messages-group"> <div class="messages"> <div class="message yissod"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Yissod</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">The sky</div> </div> </div> <div class="message beans"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">beans</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">every goddamn time</div> </div> </div> <div class="message tohos"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Tohos</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">guys</div> </div> </div> <div class="message prosp"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">PROSP</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content"><span class="at_mention">@Yissod</span> I fucking swear</div> </div> </div> <div class="message tohos"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Toho