&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Access&amp;nbsp;Granted&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To Dr. Taylor,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Despite your lack of professionalism towards the start of the attached document, we understand that you had gone through a struggle that would help provide insight into an otherwise unknown situation. Granted we do know about the Well but you are one of the few that was able to see the Well and not suffer ill side effects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is with this in mind that myself and the other head members of the Department of Tactical Theology have allowed you to witness the interview and verification of one Dylan Cecht - now known as PoI-91231 - until either the Well can be successfully contained or until the Department sees no more use of your expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We understand that you may require some rest, but we ask that you attend the interview that is booked on the 25th of December, at midnight. The location will be Area-38 so no need to prepare any additional materials for what comes ahead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once again, we look forward to seeing you working with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merry Christmas and happy new year from the Department of Tactical Theology,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Darnell Fortin,&lt;br /&gt;
Assistant Director of Personnel at Area-27.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
