&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;wiki-email&quot;&gt;moc.ytpme|s934hgf#moc.ytpme|s934hgf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;wiki-email&quot;&gt;noitadnuof.TENPiCS|eciffo85O#noitadnuof.TENPiCS|eciffo85O&lt;/span&gt; (Protected Account)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Greetings Ms Saw,&lt;br /&gt;
Yes, I know your name. I know a lot about you, you&#039;re an interesting woman. I also know that you recently approved a project of mass neutralisation surrounding &#039;low-hume entities&#039;. Your methods have caused mass panic in only two days. While I&#039;m sure you have a &#039;good reason&#039; for this obvious atrocity, I find that the only way to approve this is by pure malice. For this reason, I am responsible for the bombing you have recently witnesses. It will happen again if you do not follow these demands carefully:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Appeal your decision to the overseer council. Vote against the decision, get another council member to vote with you. Then, veto any attempt to investigate the blast. You may tell other members of the council our &lt;em&gt;arrangement&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yours Truly, X&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Should intermittent vengeance arm again his red right hand to plague us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O5-8 closed the email, sending another to the full council.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span&gt;SCiPNET Database&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;wiki-email&quot;&gt;noitadnuof.TENPiCS|eciffo85O#noitadnuof.TENPiCS|eciffo85O&lt;/span&gt; (Protected Account)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To:&lt;/strong&gt; Overseer Command (Group)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There&#039;s been a bombing. The Insurgency is responsible. There will be more to come. Get ready.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O5-8&lt;br /&gt;
