&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-650172-2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;2&lt;/a&gt;. Liberian dollars. $1,000,000 LRD ≈ $6,200 USD.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
