				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/petition-to-ban-margssentif</guid>
				<title>Petition To Ban Margssentif</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/petition-to-ban-margssentif</link>
				<description>


&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tabview-0f932a1165e0a4695e23c3e9e910bf26&quot; class=&quot;yui-navset&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;yui-nav&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;selected&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Introduction to Margssentif and his crimes&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Awful Writing&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Poor fools who were tricked into making things for Fitnessgram&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;yui-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tab-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;Site admins, please heed this call to ban this filthy ingrate. Cast him into the fire! Beat him senseless with the might of the Banhammer! Strike him down!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Margssentif, who is also known as Fitnessgram in the IRC Chat (More like FitnessLAME, am I right?), where he asks stupid questions and says stupider things, is a major dickwad and I frankly cannot stand him. The audacity of this bastard is intolerable.&lt;br /&gt;
For too long has this asshole harassed, irritated, and generally fucked with everyone on the Site. His handsomeness and massive, bulging muscles are too vexing for me to handle.&lt;br /&gt;
This is why I have made this page, for the collective good of the community, to permanently banish this scumbag from the face of the earth. Hopefully I shall never be made to feel inferior by his sheer bodaciousness ever again.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please like this article if you support the immediate ban of Margssentif (and his chiselled jawline) from this site. If you don&#039;t want him to be banned, blink twice if you are being held at gunpoint.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, use the discussion page to share your worst experiences with Margssentif. That prick&#039;s immense ego needs to be taken down a size or two. I&#039;ll start:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My worst experience with Margssentif is looking in the mirror each morning and seeing how pathetic I am compared to that paragon of might.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tab-0-1&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not only is Margssentif handsome and modest, he is also an awful writer. Just look at this awful writing! So many comma splices and run-on sentences! Margssentif is just asking to be banned at this point.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;Show&amp;nbsp;cursed&amp;nbsp;writing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;Dear&amp;nbsp;God&amp;nbsp;my&amp;nbsp;eyes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tab-0-2&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Margssentif somehow managed to get other users to make things for him. Doubtlessly they did it out of fear of his &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: line-through;&quot;&gt;colossal muscles and beautiful features&lt;/span&gt; or hope that he’d leave them alone for a few minutes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610226471&quot; alt=&quot;Calibri Bold&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold&quot;  &gt;Calibri Bold&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTLYHy3Aqqw&amp;amp;t=3s%20reads%20Margssentif%E2%80%99s%20SCP-5086.%20Cover%20your%20eyes,%20ears,%20and%20nose%20so%20none%20of%20the%20incredibly%20mundane%20writing%20gets%20in.&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTLYHy3Aqqw&amp;amp;t=3s reads Margssentif’s SCP-5086. Cover your eyes, ears, and nose so none of the incredibly mundane writing gets in.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image-container aligncenter&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/petition-to-ban-margssentif/Arorangi.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/petition-to-ban-margssentif/Arorangi.jpg/medium.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Arorangi.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610226471&quot; alt=&quot;Alces_alces&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces&quot;  &gt;Alces_alces&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; had to be forced to make this art for Margssentif during the 2020 Holiday exchange because of course, no one would do that willingly&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[[div class=&amp;quot;licensebox&amp;quot;]]&lt;br /&gt;
