						 <div id="wiki-tabview-75e51db38cfb7d657eba7b5270aab58b" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Introduction to Margssentif and his crimes</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Awful Writing</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Poor fools who were tricked into making things for Fitnessgram</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <h2><span>Site admins, please heed this call to ban this filthy ingrate. Cast him into the fire! Beat him senseless with the might of the Banhammer! Strike him down!!</span></h2> <p>Margssentif, who is also known as Fitnessgram in the IRC Chat (More like FitnessLAME, am I right?), where he asks stupid questions and says stupider things, is a major dickwad and I frankly cannot stand him. The audacity of this bastard is intolerable.<br /> For too long has this asshole harassed, irritated, and generally fucked with everyone on the Site. His handsomeness and massive, bulging muscles are too vexing for me to handle.<br /> This is why I have made this page, for the collective good of the community, to permanently banish this scumbag from the face of the earth. Hopefully I shall never be made to feel inferior by his sheer bodaciousness ever again.</p> <p>Please like this article if you support the immediate ban of Margssentif (and his chiselled jawline) from this site. If you don't want him to be banned, blink twice if you are being held at gunpoint.</p> <p>Also, use the discussion page to share your worst experiences with Margssentif. That prick's immense ego needs to be taken down a size or two. I'll start:</p> <blockquote> <p>My worst experience with Margssentif is looking in the mirror each morning and seeing how pathetic I am compared to that paragon of might.</p> </blockquote> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none"> <p>Not only is Margssentif handsome and modest, he is also an awful writer. Just look at this awful writing! So many comma splices and run-on sentences! Margssentif is just asking to be banned at this point.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Show&nbsp;cursed&nbsp;writing</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Dear&nbsp;God&nbsp;my&nbsp;eyes</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none"> <p>Margssentif somehow managed to get other users to make things for him. Doubtlessly they did it out of fear of his <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">colossal muscles and beautiful features</span> or hope that he’d leave them alone for a few minutes.</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226471" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTLYHy3Aqqw&amp;t=3s%20reads%20Margssentif%E2%80%99s%20SCP-5086.%20Cover%20your%20eyes,%20ears,%20and%20nose%20so%20none%20of%20the%20incredibly%20mundane%20writing%20gets%20in.">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTLYHy3Aqqw&amp;t=3s reads Margssentif’s SCP-5086. Cover your eyes, ears, and nose so none of the incredibly mundane writing gets in.</a></p> <hr /> <div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/petition-to-ban-margssentif/Arorangi.jpg"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/petition-to-ban-margssentif/Arorangi.jpg/medium.jpg" alt="Arorangi.jpg" class="image" /></a></div> <p><sup><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226471" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span> had to be forced to make this art for Margssentif during the 2020 Holiday exchange because of course, no one would do that willingly</sup></p> </div> </div> </div> <br /> <div class="licensebox"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">‡&nbsp;Licensing&nbsp;/&nbsp;Citation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">‡&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;Licensing&nbsp;/&nbsp;Citation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Cite this page as:</p> <p>For more information, see <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/licensing-guide">Licensing Guide</a>.<br /> <strong>Licensing Disclosures</strong></p> <div class="content-separator" style="display: none:"></div> <p><strong>Image 1</strong></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Filename:</strong> Arorangi.jpg<br /> <strong>Name:</strong> N/A<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226471" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY-SA 3.0<br /> <strong>Source Link:</strong> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/local--files/petition-to-ban-margssentif/Arorangi.jpg">The SCP Wiki</a></p> </blockquote> <div class="content-separator" style="display: none