&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following article is a sequel to &lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5936&quot;&gt;SCP-5936&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/critter-profile-sparky&quot;&gt;Critter Profile: Sparky!&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5890&quot;&gt;SCP-5890&lt;/a&gt;. Whilst you can read it on its own, it&#039;s highly recommended you read all of the previous installments to get this article in its fullest.&lt;/p&gt;
